            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Como sabemos que este loop para?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepGoing = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepGoing {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Just keep swimming&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" keepGoing = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"Just keep swimming\" /></content></output></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">A variável <code>keepGoing</code> é atualizada para <code>false</code> dentro do bloco de código</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">Não sabemos se o loop para</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">A variável <code>keepGoing</code> é atualizada para <code>false</code> dentro do bloco de código.</p></body></html>"
